{"tid":1134311,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯擬用1.2億歐元購入馬體會門將奧比歷","createTime":"2019-05-01T17:00:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T18:53:46.000Z","uid":186071,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b0458eb82f936fad5819ef3beed391492747ec49","tid":1134311,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T17:00:29.000Z","msg":"據《ESPN》報道，「紅魔鬼」曼聯今夏積極考慮在轉會市場大破慳囊，將計劃斥資1.2億歐元（約10.5億港元）啟動西甲球隊馬德里體育會門將奧比歷（Jan Oblak）的贖身條款，令迪基亞頓時變得不明朗。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，現年26歲的奧比歷為斯洛文尼亞國腳，他雖然在今個月與馬體會續約至2023年，但是其贖身條款的價碼僅增加了2,000萬歐元至目前的1.2億歐元，曼聯相信用這個價錢，能夠羅致被譽為世上最出色門將之一的奧比歷來說，仍然是非常超值。"},{"pid":"7388c1ddb390e0de7c37b570ccb7bf689ced2926","tid":1134311,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T17:02:01.000Z","msg":"派幾下膠就咁"},{"pid":"4a143ebbb3d15b1b4f02209fee8cec1d2938d9fc","tid":1134311,"uid":51701,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T17:07:43.000Z","msg":"令迪基亞頓時變得不明朗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n體育老師教中文?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f503bfb4fca8312bac6661f6f8afb0a02d6f77c7","tid":1134311,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T17:22:41.000Z","msg":"羅美路唔夠班?"},{"pid":"1952dce15905ac1a332a2f4a6825d90d5e66de68","tid":1134311,"uid":1303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T17:25:11.000Z","msg":"原來球會都會扭屎忽花，想嚇ddg <br />\n<br />\n想知如果oblak 又話要500k週薪佢點拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9148d2bd02248ccdc853d905b384ec404a5a1758","tid":1134311,"uid":38189,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T17:26:41.000Z","msg":"曼聯廢關個龍撚事咩"},{"pid":"a2f9843084b7ce76099b36bf0cbc68a0b0730688","tid":1134311,"uid":160589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T17:28:23.000Z","m